condition.narrative: At least 3 months prior to commencing any civil works in Proj. Corridors (i) prepare a proposed WP & budget for treatment ofblackspots in the following 12-m period; (ii) furnish said WP for review
Establish & maintain the following organizations with terms of ref., staffing &other resources (a) A Consultative Council; (b) AProject Steering Committee; (c) A Sub-PMU in each Participating Agency
Every 12 months (i) prepare a WP for treatment of blackspots in the Project Corridors in the next succeeding 12-m period; (ii)provide each such work plan for review
NTSC to maintain, the Traffic Safety Project Management Unit, established within the National Traffic Safety Committee &responsible for coordinating & overseeing implementation of Project activities
prepare & furnish on/ab. Mar 31 & Sep 31 each year, starting on Mar 31, 2006, a semi-annual report on the progress achieved &setting out the measures recommended to ensure efficient carrying of proj.
